Introduction¶

This is a datset of Proser Loans that contains 113937 loans with 81 variables on each loan, including loan amount, borrower rate, current loan status, borrower income, and many others. We will use Python data science and data visualization libraries to explore the datasets variables and understand the datas structure, patterns and relationships. We will also take our main findings from our exploration and convey them to others through an explanatory analysis.I'll be analyzing Univariate,Bivariate and Mulivariate analysis for a clearer understanding.
